// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0702 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: dd889892-4cd0-5e82-a7d5-80ebcbe5b34d

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:1* OR ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
